 OK fellow warrior brothers/sisters, I have a question for ya:<br>
<br>
I've recently got a Sunderfury from Hate which is an awesome 2HS weapon and to satisfy my own curiosity of the 2HS vs 1HS taunt issue and have found that I don't have any problems keeping a mobs attention when using it vs my 1HS weapons (Wurmslayer and Kunzar).  (As a side note, I have a Hangmans noose for haste as well)<br>
<br>
Has anyone else tried this to see if the taunt myth is true?  I'd like to hear other warrior take on this issue.<br>
<br>
Thanks in advance....<br>
<br>
Jarrel<br>
Barbarian Warrior of the 52nd Blade<br>
The Unity of Justice <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utalaena.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Talaena</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.dangermouse.org/images/penfold/funny3.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Where's my Tang? </span><br>  Posts: 2730<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/26/01 10:01:28 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.dangermouse.org/images/penfold/funny3.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   \</span><hr size=1> I know it's not totally relevant given my level, but:<br>
<br>
at 34 I find my most effective taunting weapon is my Mith Staff. <br>
<br>
I was just looking at Copeland's Weap Analyzer and:<br>
<br>
16.13 SPM 561 DPM for mith staff<br>
24.20 SPM 513 DPM for nathsar greatsword<br>
38.11 SPM 490 DPM for my icetooth &amp; gleaming ss<br>
46.06 SPM 468 DPM for 2 yaks<br>
<br>
<br>
Now, those are just numbers, I know. However, I have listed them in my PERCIEVED taunt effectiveness, sans procs (too low for yaks). My mith staff really does taunt noticably more than anything else I own. <br>
<br>
Copeland's thingy (technical term) has a nice feature that allows you to find weapons that meet or exceed certain Dam / min figures. So, given 2 Lammies, you can show what 2hs weapons have an equal or greater amount of DPM. <br>
<br>
Yes, they are just numbers, but based on my personal (and limited) experience,  I would bet that equipping a 2hs sword that has similar DPM to 2 lammies would produce the same type of taunt.<br>
<br>
I can outfit myself with 2 gnoll hide lariats(3/10), and I sure as hell am NOT taunting that bugger off of anything. I've had a dead rhino corpse draw more attention than my 2 lariats. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
There is my most unknowledgable opinion of things. I'm just watching a report run aimlessly int he background, so I'm bored. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukallikamerov.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kalli Kamerov</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Protector of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 477<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/26/01 11:53:20 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://images.honesty.com/imagedata/h/895/90/28959015.jpg width = 135 height = 184></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: \</span><hr size=1> That's 'cause gnoll hide lariats are 3 / 20 Talaena <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
From my very unscientific survey done in Chardok last Thursday, Drahx seemed to be delivering more taunt using his Sarnak Battlehammer (30/40 2hb) over his spined dragon claws (10/21 1hs) and some 9/25 sword.<br>
<br>
I imagine that Aayana's Quickening haste had a bit to do with that though....<br>
<br>
Also on a hate raid a month or two ago Ffawsip was raving in group that he was doing much better taunting with a 2hs (this was around the agro chance patch).<br>
<br>
In conclusion...  personal experience &gt; what someone types on a message board. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Kalli Kamerov<br>
55th Enchantress<br>
Poison Arrow. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utalaena.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Talaena</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.dangermouse.org/images/penfold/funny3.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Where's my Tang? </span><br>  Posts: 2737<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/27/01 9:01:56 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.dangermouse.org/images/penfold/funny3.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: \</span><hr size=1> 3/10 3/20 what's a few ticks of delay. So I was confused. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
